    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The House of Toys is a game developed by Old School Bros, a duo of video game and horror genre enthusiasts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321000/extras/69f2048e5b8e8c1fdf6d508b2e43d3b0.poster.avif?t=1764271091\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321000/extras/69f2048e5b8e8c1fdf6d508b2e43d3b0.webm?t=1764271091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321000/extras/69f2048e5b8e8c1fdf6d508b2e43d3b0.mp4?t=1764271091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game's mission is to free the soul of the cursed toy, day after day, game after game. But be careful—each game can be different. You will earn rewards that make your work more satisfying, allow you to improve your room, and help you discover secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The House of Toys is divided into several phases in each game.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Phase 1:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Investigate – Explore the mansion, searching for clues to help you identify the toy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321000/extras/cdfb1417b8525df3d38a037fdcf5ac93.poster.avif?t=1764271091\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321000/extras/cdfb1417b8525df3d38a037fdcf5ac93.webm?t=1764271091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321000/extras/cdfb1417b8525df3d38a037fdcf5ac93.mp4?t=1764271091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Phase 2:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Puzzles and Action – While avoiding the cursed toy, you’ll need to solve puzzles that grant you the power to free its soul.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321000/extras/70de2abfc54c6cb4a3c018021fb1ccb2.poster.avif?t=1764271091\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321000/extras/70de2abfc54c6cb4a3c018021fb1ccb2.webm?t=1764271091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321000/extras/70de2abfc54c6cb4a3c018021fb1ccb2.mp4?t=1764271091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Phase 3:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stealth – You’ll need to be cautious and stealthy to use your new power and release the toy’s soul.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321000/extras/354f10201d49cb7039d352f8afaa22c8.poster.avif?t=1764271091\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321000/extras/354f10201d49cb7039d352f8afaa22c8.webm?t=1764271091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321000/extras/354f10201d49cb7039d352f8afaa22c8.mp4?t=1764271091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you dare to discover the true origin of the curse?</p>",
